snippet.title: Quick Mathematical Card Trick
snippet.description:
Colm Mulcahy’s Mathematical Card Magic: Fifty-Two New Effects
US AMAZON
http://www.amazon.com/Mathematical-Card-Magic-Fifty-Two-Effects/dp/1466509767?_encoding=UTF8&tag=stanupmath-20

UK AMAZON
https://www.amazon.co.uk/Mathematical-Card-Magic-Fifty-Two-Effects/dp/1466509767/ref=sr_1_1?_encoding=UTF8&tag=stanupmath-21

What's in side the spherical dice? Stay tuned (as such).

CORRECTIONS:
Yes, I accidentally said "eight" instead of "four". I caught it just in time during the edit to put in a text correction, but not soon enough to be able to re-film it.

Music by Howard Carter
Design by Simon Wright

MATT PARKER: Stand-up Mathematician
Website: http://standupmaths.com/
Book: http://makeanddo4D.com/
Nerdy maths toys: http://mathsgear.co.uk/
